<div class="container-fluid px-4">
    <h1 class="mt-4 tituloverde">Tamizaje Dermatológico</h1>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <div class="left-content">
                <i class="fas fa-table me-1"></i>
                Cuestionario de Tamizaje Dermatológico
            </div>
            <div>
                <button class="btn position-relative" style="background-color: #793B8E; color: white; padding:0px"
                    id="btnGrabar" onclick="Grabar()">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-floppy-disk" style="margin: 8px 12px;"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body " style="max-height: 70vh; overflow-y: auto; ">
            <input type="text" id="nuncom" style="display: none;" value="0">
            <input type="text" id="codpru_id" style="display: none;" value="16">
            <input type="text" id="soexa" style="display: none;" value="016">
            <div id="formPreguntas">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>1. ¿Sufre Ud. Enfermedades de la piel?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre1" id="ce_pre1S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre1S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre1" id="ce_pre1N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre1N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>2. ¿Actualmente tiene alguna lesión (ampolla, escama, rascado)?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline ">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre2" id="ce_pre2S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre2S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre2" id="ce_pre2N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre2N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>3. ¿Presenta algún cambio en la coloración de la piel?
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre3" id="ce_pre3S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre3S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre3" id="ce_pre3N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre3N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>4. ¿Estas lesiones se repiten varias veces al año?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre4" id="ce_pre4S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre4S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre4" id="ce_pre4N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre4N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>5. ¿Ud. Tiene enrojecimiento en alguna zona del cuerpo?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre5" id="ce_pre5S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre5S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre5" id="ce_pre5N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre5N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>6. ¿Tiene comezón?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre6" id="ce_pre6S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre6S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre6" id="ce_pre6N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre6N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>7. ¿Presenta hinchazón en parte de su cuerpo?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre7" id="ce_pre7S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre7S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre7" id="ce_pre7N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre7N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>8. ¿Sufre de rinitis Alérgica o ASMA?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre8" id="ce_pre8S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre8S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre8" id="ce_pre8N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre8N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>9. ¿Usa EPP?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre9" id="ce_pre9S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre9S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre9" id="ce_pre9N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre9N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>10. ¿Presenta cambios en la uña?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre10" id="ce_pre10S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre10S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre10" id="ce_pre10N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre10N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>11. ¿Está tomando algún medicación?</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre11" id="ce_pre11S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre11S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre11" id="ce_pre11N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre11N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row body1 mb-3" id="divMedicamentos" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <label for="ce_pre11_rpta" class="labels ms-1">Describa en caso de tener alguna respuesta
                            positiva</label>
                        <textarea name="" id="ce_pre11_rpta" class="form-control form-control-sm"
                            placeholder="Indique que medicamentos"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>12. ¿El paciente al examen físico presenta alguna lesión sugerente a Dermatopatía</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre12" id="ce_pre12S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre12S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre12" id="ce_pre12N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre12N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 ms-1">
                        <p>13. ¿El paciente necesita ser evaluado por médico dermatólogo para la realización de las
                            siguientes pruebas: Prueba de sensibilidad mucocutánea, Luz de Wood y Maniobra de
                            Nikolsky?
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre13" id="ce_pre13S" value="SI">
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre13S">Si</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="ce_pre13" id="ce_pre13N" value="NO"
                                checked>
                            <label class="form-check-label" for="ce_pre13N">No</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{> cie10 }}
            {{> recomendaciones }}
            {{> documentoadicionales }}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

